'''''Majuba: Heuwel van Duiwe''''' '''(Majuba: Hill ya inuma),''' ni filimi yakozwe muri 1968 muri Afurika y'Epfo iyi film iyoborwa na  Dawidi Millin afatanyije na  Roscoe C. Behrmann na Hyman Kirstein.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Roland Robinson, Reinet Maasdorp, na Patrick Mynhardt mu bakinnyi ba mbere hamwe na Siegfried Mynhardt, Anna Neethling-Pohl na Morné Coetzer mu nshingano zabo.  

Filime yatewe inkunga nibyabaye mu Ntambara ya mbere ya Anglo-Boer, Intambara yo ku musozi wa Majuba . Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.

Filime yumwimerere yo gusohora sinema yakoresheje amasaha agera kuri atatu nyamara abayagurisha baho bagabanije firime kugirango berekane burimunsi kuko yari ikunzwe cyane: verisiyo yagufi ni ibisigaye byose byaciwe mbere kandi amashusho ntiyigeze abikwa.

